Just thought I'd let ya know, I'm not sure how you applied the hair mask but with conditioners & masks they are only designed for the mid lengths & ends of your hair as that's where your hair needs the most focus, and that could be why your hair feels greasy. I'm an ex hairdresser so just thought I'd put my advice in. Also don't use too much as this can also make your hair feel greasy.
